<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When using setDatePattern on a Dojo DateTextBox form element yy pattern behaves the same as yyyy even though Unicode Date Format Pattern specifies that yy should produce a year pattern with a maximum of length 2.</p>

<p>Example:
setDatePattern('dd-MMM-yy')</p>

<p>behaves like</p>

<p>setDatePattern('dd-MMM-yyyy')</p>

    </div>
</div>

